import { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import axios from 'axios' import "./propertyList.css"; const PropertyList = () => { const [hoteltype, setHotetype] = useState(); useEffect(() => { axios.get('http://localhost:5000/hotels/hoteltype').then(result => { setHotetype(result.data) }).catch(err => console.log(err)); }, []) console.log(hoteltype[0].count) return (
{/*

Hotels

{hoteltype[0].count} hotels

Apartments

{hoteltype[1].count} hotels

Resorts

{hoteltype[2].count} hotels

Villas

{hoteltype[3].count} hotels

Cabins

{hoteltype[4].count} hotels

*/}
); }; export default PropertyList;
